December 1, 2025, read first time and referred to Committee on Courts and Criminal Code.
December 2, 2025, reassigned to Committee on Judiciary.
January 12, 2026, amended, reported — Do Pass.
January 15, 2026, read second time, ordered engrossed.
January 16, 2026, engrossed.
January 20, 2026, read third time, passed. Yeas 88, nays 2.
